room_title: Escape room "The Source" by Roswell Escapes LLC in Roswell
room_description: You have recently received a mysterious notebook containing a map to Dr. Taggert's remote and long-closed high desert cabin. This famous physicist was working in the Magic program for the US government before the war. He was supposed to decrypting the new Japanese code PURPLE but during testing, but couldn't figure out the source transmitting the code. Can you solve the mystery of The Source?
